<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id" class="h-full">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %> — FTI Project</title>
  <!-- Basecoat UI CSS (Lokal dari node_modules) -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/basecoat/basecoat.min.css" />
  <!-- Basecoat UI JS (Lokal dari node_modules) -->
  <script src="/basecoat/js/basecoat.min.js" defer></script>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;900&display=swap');
    :root {
      --bc-font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      --fti-blue: #70869e;
      --fti-blue-dark: #5b6f85;
      --bc-color-primary: var(--fti-blue);
      --bc-border-radius: 8px;
    }
    body {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--bc-font-family);
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      color: #334155;
    }
    .container {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 420px;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px -10px rgba(112, 134, 158, 0.15);
    }
    .error-code {
      font-size: 5rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      line-height: 1;
      margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1e293b;
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    }
    p {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .btn-dark {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
      background-color: var(--fti-blue);
      color: white;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-dark:hover { background-color: var(--fti-blue-dark); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Optional: Area untuk Logo FTI -->
    <img src="/images/fti-logo.png" alt="Logo FTI Unand" style="height: 60px; width: auto; max-width: 100%; object-fit: contain; margin: 0 auto 1rem auto; display: block;" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
    
    <div class="error-code">403</div>
    <h1>Akses Ditolak</h1>
    <p>Maaf, Anda tidak memiliki hak akses untuk membuka halaman ini. Halaman ini hanya tersedia untuk peran (*role*) tertentu.</p>
    
    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-dark">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
      Kembali ke Dashboard
    </a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
